c|date=September 2016}}{{BLP sources|date=September 2016}}}}\n{{Infobox musical artist\n| name             = Sokun Nisa<br/>({{Plain link|//km.wikipedia.org/wiki/\u179f\u17bb\u1782\u1793\u17d2\u1792_\u1793\u17b7\u179f\u17b6 | \u179f\u17bb\u1782\u1793\u17d2\u1792 \u1793\u17b7\u179f\u17b6}})\n| image            = Sokun Nisa.jpg\n| background       = solo_singer\n| birth_date       = {{birth date and age|1983|5|01}}\n| birth_place      = [[Krati\u00e9 Province|Kratie]], Cambodia\n| origin           = Cambodia\n| instrument       = Voice\n| genre            = \n| occupation       = Singer, actress\n| years_active     = 1999\u2013present\n| label            = Rasmey Steung Songkae<br/>(2003\u20132005)<br> Spark Music<br/>(2006)<br> Rasmey Hang Meas Production<br/>(2007\u20132011)<br> Town Production<br/>(2012\u20132015)<br> Rasmey Hang Meas Production<br/>(2016\u2013present)\n| website          = \n| birth_name       = Pon Sokunthea\n| alias            = Sokun Nisa\n}}\n'''Sokun Nisa''' ({{lang-km|{{Plain link|//km.wikipedia.org/wiki/\u179f\u17bb\u1782\u1793\u17d2\u1792_\u1793\u17b7\u179f\u17b6 | \u179f\u17bb\u1782\u1793\u17d2\u1792 \u1793\u17b7\u179f\u17b6}}}}; born May 1, 1983) is a popular singer in [[Cambodia]]. In 2003, she started her career as a singer with Rasmey Steung Sangke Production. Currently she is a singer under Rasmey Hang Meas Production. \n\nIn 2017, she made her acting debut on television in a remake of Korean drama [[Autumn in My Heart]] as Lead Actress of the series.\n\n==Discography==\n\n=== Solo albums ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n! colspan=\"2\" |Album Title\n!Vol\n!Production\n|-\n|2009\n|No Other ''<sup>(LIT.)</sup>''\n|\u1782\u17d2\u1798\u17b6\u1793\u17a2\u17d2\u1793\u1780\u1795\u17d2\u179f\u17c1\u1784\n|394\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Rasmey Hang Meas Production\n|-\n|2010\n|Little Girl\n|\n|423\n|-\n|2015\n|Love you is my karma ''<sup>(LIT.)</sup>''\n|\u179f\u17d2\u179a\u17a1\u17b6\u1789\u17cb\u1794\u1784\u1787\u17b6\u1780\u1798\u17d2\u1798\u17